snippet.title: Alphabear Trailer, v2
snippet.description:
Alphabear is an original word puzzle game by Spry Fox! Available on iOS and Android. 

Download it for iOS here: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/alphabear-word-puzzle-game/id930003798
Download it for Android here: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.spryfox.alphabear
